<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
   

<center><h4>Leave request cancellation by your direct reportee</h4></center>

<p>A leave request has been cancelled by <b> <%= @leave_request.employee.try(:prefix).to_s+' '+@leave_request.employee.first_name.to_s+' '+@leave_request.employee.last_name.to_s %></b> from date<b> <%= @leave_request.start_date.to_date %></b> to<b> <%= @leave_request.end_date.to_date%>.</b></p>
 
<h4>Requester Details :-</h4>
 
<p>Employee ID :- <%= @leave_request.employee.manual_employee_code %></p>
 
<h4>Details of the Leave :-</h4>
 
<p>Total Number of days :-  <%= @leave_request.leave_count %></p>
 
<p>Leave Reason :- <%= @leave_request.reason %></p>
  </body>
</html>
